## In terminal
• npm create astro@latest
• y to proceed
• ./tremendous-trappist
• include sample files
• install dependencies
• yes to write typescript
• Strict
• Initialize new git repos
• npm install -g astro
• npm fund
• npm run build (error)
• npm audit fix
• npm install @astrojs/image
• npm cache clean --force
• npx astro clear-cache
• npm update
• npm run build 
• npm run start

## Updating code in GitHub
• git status
• git add
• git status
• git branch dev && git switch dev
• git push origin dev
• go to your github account to remote and create a pull request
• delete
